tent><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/10/24153572/the-rogue-prince-of-persia-release-postponed-hades-2" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/10/24153572/the-rogue-prince-of-persia-release-postponed-hades-2</id><author><name>阿什·帕里什</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-05-10T12:25:15-04:00</published><updated> 2024-05-10T12:25:15-04:00</updated><title> 500 美元以下可以买到的最好的智能手机</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;来自 Google、Apple 和 Samsung 的手机，背景为彩色插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/t2Mje1exJnZyEZRBhf5hrBEQbvE=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/67732462/226422_K_Radtke_budget_phone_buying_guide.1 3.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;如果您知道如何选择优先事项，现在您就可以花不到 500 美元购买一台出色的设备。&lt;/em>; |图片：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;你不可能以这个价格拥有一切，但你可以获得一部很棒的智能手机。无论您想要 iPhone、120Hz 屏幕还是防水，您都有选择。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21420196/best-budget-smartphone-便宜&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/21420196/best-budget-smartphone-cheap" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/21420196/best-budget-smartphone-cheap</id><author><name>艾莉森·约翰逊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-05-10T12:17:31-04:00</published><updated> 2024-05-10T12:17:31-04:00</updated><title>苹果可能会将人工智能转录引入语音备忘录和笔记</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;黄色和青色背景上的 Apple 徽标插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/FrWH7G2tigVVLBhYtUjikL6D6Mw=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73339394/STK071_apple_K_Radtke_02.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;插图：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;0aCMgn&quot;>;根据 &lt;a href= 的说法，苹果公司在 iPhone 上的人工智能计划可以为其语音备忘录和便笺应用程序带来实时转录功能“https://appleinsider.com/articles/24/05/10/apple-set-to-deliver-ai-assistant-for-transcribing-summarizing-meetings-and-lectures&quot;>;来自 &lt;em>;AppleInsider 的报告&lt; /em>;&lt;/a>;。这项新功能预计将随 iOS 18 一起发布，据报道，您可以在任一应用程序中查看正在运行的录音转录。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;WQySP3&quot;>;虽然 Notes 目前不允许您录制音频， &lt;a href=&quot;https://appleinsider.com/articles/24/04/17/apple-notes-in-ios-18-looks-to-up-the-ante-with-microsoft-onenote&quot;>;一个单独的来自 &lt;em>;AppleInsider&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>; 的传言表明，苹果也计划在 iOS 18 中添加此功能。这两个应用程序中的音频转录对于学生或记者来说听起来特别方便，他们可以节省转录冗长的讲座或采访的时间。对于那些只想快速查看语音备忘录而无需收听录音的人来说，它也应该很有帮助。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;lsTn7G&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;更好的 Siri 即将到来：苹果的研究对其人工智能的评价计划&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/5/24147995/apple-siri-ai-research-chatbot-creativity&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;更多详细信息苹果在 iOS 18 中的人工智能计划&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/3/24148282/apple-ai-iphone-ios-18-plans-ajax&quot;}]}&#39; >;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;MZBonZ&quot;>;至于...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/ 5/10/24153618/apple-ai-transcription-notes-voice-memos&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/10/24153618/apple-ai-transcription-notes-voice-memos" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/10/24153618/apple-ai-transcription-notes-voice-memos</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-05-10T11:25:10-04:00</published><updated> 2024-05-10T11:25:10-04:00</updated><title> 《猩球崛起3》是对该系列过去的华丽回响</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/vZ_twz_B_fR5A5egEvQ5D0oHJ9U=/683x0:3257x1716/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73339215 /KPA_TP3_00087206.0.jpeg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片：20 世纪工作室&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;《猩球崛起3》混音了该系列之前电影的节奏，讲述了一个关于神话如何演变的故事.&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;